---
title: Guardian Skip
hidden: false
---
Guardian Skip is using the [Drop AFK Method](/ds1remaster/drop-afk) to Enter the boss arena and allow the player to skip the bossfight. The skip is really precise and require frame perfect inputs.

\
This skip was found by **San & splee5556** in Febuary 2026.

## **External Resources**

Demonstration [https://youtu.be/68AQBOO9mCw](https://youtu.be/68AQBOO9mCw) by San on YouTube.
